><a href=\"/wiki/The_New_York_Times\" title=\"The New York Times\">The New York Times</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 May</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=The+Jews%2C+a+History+in+So+Many%2C+Many+Words&amp;rft.date=2014-03-10&amp;rft.au=Garner%2C+Dwight&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2014%2F03%2F11%2Fbooks%2Fsimon-schamas-the-story-of-the-jews.html%3F_r%3D0&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Story+of+the+Jews+%28book%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Williams-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Williams_9-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a href=\"/wiki/Rowan_Williams\" title=\"Rowan Williams\">Williams, Rowan</a> (7 October 2017). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.newstatesman.com/culture/books/2017/10/simon-schamas-jewish-history-immensely-erudite-and-compulsively-readable\">\"Simon Schama's Jewish history is immensely erudite&#160;\u2013 and compulsively readable\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_New_Statesman\" title=\"The New Statesman\">The New Statesman</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 October</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+Statesman&amp;rft.atitle=Simon+Schama%27s+Jewish+history+is+immensely+erudite+%E2%80%93+and+compulsively+readable&amp;rft.date=2017-10-07&amp;rft.au=Williams%2C+Rowan&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newstatesman.com%2Fculture%2Fbooks%2F2017%2F10%2Fsimon-schamas-jewish-history-immensely-erudite-and-compulsively-readable&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Story+of+the+J